danish trade in balanc in februari denmark 's balanc of payment on current account wa provis put at zero in februari , against a 181 mln crown surplu in januari and a 1.5 billion deficit in februari 1986 , the nation statist offic said . export rose to 13.94 billion crown in februari from 12.53 billion in januari , against 14.16 billion in februari last year . februari import rose to 13.94 billion from 12.35 billion in januari , against 15.67 billion in februari 1986. the februari figur provis give a trade surplu for 1987 of 180 mln crown , against a 3.04 billion deficit in the same 1986 period .